he month of idle time off Peru on previous voyage and split this cost with Norient ($1250 for us in expenses) Mariflex (pump rental) bill in line with estimate.  Heating $25k vs $20 est.  Vessel has an issue with ODME and retained slops onboard that had to be pumped off.  $45k is this bill but since we believe it is malfunctioning we will push 2/3rds of the bill back to owners ($30k shown as rebill)  Pumping at Houston coincided with a \u201Ccold\u201D front dropping temps to around 6C and took around 12 days to finish discharge.  Vessel maintained 100 psi at the rail but rate dropped to 100m3/hr or less at times.  We expect a bit of a dispute on demurrage but results shows 6 days added here ($115k @ 18.5kpday).\n*** Vessel also experienced an allision just after pumping as per Ethan\u2019s update attached.  Ultimately class approved a repair to be done alongside layberth after discharge completed and we made it to next HydroAlunorte a little late but they maintained us thankfully.  There will be some offhire bunkers discussed for next voyage."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-11-19T14:59:58.737","modifiedByFull":"Butcher, Carol","remark":"PNL decrease -49281 - remove estimate for balance of freight"},{"modifiedDate":"2021-11-10T21:39:22.117","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Demurrage billed for 6 days due discharge. Vessel met 100 psi at the rail throughout."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-11-04T17:51:46.043","modifiedByFull":"Butcher, Carol","remark":"PNL increase \u002B2213 - balance of freight based  on Outturn figures which were approx 930 mt more than B/L quantity"},{"modifiedDate":"2021-11-01T20:31:29.87","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Slops removal at Houston was required - rebilling majority to Owners due faulty ODME"},{"modifiedDate":"2021-10-27T14:01:31.73","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"$826 $/ton bunkers stem in Panama.."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-10-26T20:00:56.633","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"bunkers saved from Panama to Houston"},{"modifiedDate":"2021-10-21T21:00:00.8","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"PC transit earlier than expected reducing voyage days"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}